{
  "message": "Overhaul SpotlightSearch with animations and featured prompts\n\nComprehensive redesign of the command palette experience:\n\nAnimation improvements:\n- Integrate framer-motion for smooth enter/exit animations\n- Replace CSS animate-in with motion.div using scale (0.96->1) and\n  opacity transitions for both backdrop and dialog\n- Use AnimatePresence for clean exit animations\n\nEmpty state enhancement:\n- Display featured prompts when search query is empty instead of\n  generic \"Start typing\" message\n- Add StarIcon for featured section header with uppercase label\n- Each featured prompt shows title, category badge, description,\n  and a preview snippet of the prompt content\n\nVisual refinements:\n- Increase border-radius to rounded-2xl for softer appearance\n- Enhanced shadow: 25px blur with subtle 1px border simulation\n- Add CopyIcon and CheckIcon inline SVG components for copy feedback\n- Results show copy icon on right side (emerald when copied)\n- Selected result gets indigo background tint and colored title\n- Display tags (up to 3) below description for better discoverability\n- Featured prompts show star icon next to title\n\nInteraction improvements:\n- handleFeaturedSelect callback for copy-on-select behavior\n- Consistent result item layout with flex gap-3\n- Improved keyboard hint styling in footer (text-[11px])\n\nAccessibility:\n- Maintain all existing ARIA attributes and keyboard navigation\n- Proper role=\"option\" with aria-selected for all result types\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
